channel.title: Restoration Rsps - Need co that knows java -
channel.description:
Hello everyone, I started this project a while ago never really got into it. I'm looking for a co owner that's american and knows java coding. I got a real nice source and client just looking for a person thats willing to do this project with me. I also have a website (its a free domain but it works). Everything is set just a few minor fixes and we're ready for launch. Really Really want this to happen.
~~~~information about the server~~~~ -667-718 source/client
-Flawless no errors
-Want to change a few things in the source will go in to this later with established co.
~~~Co-owner information~~~
-Must be American/live in America, does not matter what timezone.
-Know how to code java. (not a basic understanding)
-preferably ages 15-20 (I'm 16)
Please note the reason I prefer you to be american is because everything will be easier. No I'm not racist
If you are wanting co - please add my skype 'angelofdeathrs1' please state that you're wanting co when you add me.
